  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Check valve guide/valve stem clearance, replace"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. Valve removal",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R002132",
          "label": "Valve removal",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "2. Check valve guide/valve stem clearance"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "2133_3.0_jpn_11238930_2.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Inspect the valve. ​ Measure the inside diameter of the valve guide and calculate the clearance between the valve guide and valve stem.",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R002132",
          "label": "Inspect the valve.",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "If the limit value is exceeded, replace the valve and valve guide as a set."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "rows": [
        [
          {
            "text": "Intake: 1",
            "colspan": 2
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "text": "Std."
          },
          {
            "text": "0.025－0.050mm"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "text": "Limit value: 1"
          },
          {
            "text": "0.08mm"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "text": "Exhaust: (1)",
            "colspan": 2
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "text": "Std."
          },
          {
            "text": "0.055－0.080mm"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "text": "Limit value: 1"
          },
          {
            "text": "0.11mm"
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. Valve guide removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "2133_3.0_jpn_11238931_2.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Valve Guide Driver 5.35 Punch the valve guide from the combustion chamber side using 9.7 (07742-0010100)."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "2. Valve Guide Mounting"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "2133_3.0_jpn_11238932_2.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Lubricate the outer circumference of the valve guide with engine oil. Valve Guide Driver 5.35 Use 9.7 to hammer in the valve guide (A)."
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Be sure to match the specified valve guide protrusion length (B)."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "rows": [
        [
          {
            "text": "Intake: 1"
          },
          {
            "text": "15.2－16.2mm"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "text": "Exhaust: (1)"
          },
          {
            "text": "16.0－17.0mm"
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "2133_3.0_jpn_11238933_2.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "3",
      "text": "Use the valve guide reamer 5.525 (07HAH-PJ70100) to correct the reaming."
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Rotate the reamer in a clockwise direction only. Do not insert or pull out the reamer while it is stopped.",
        "After reaming, measure the inside diameter of the valve guide."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "3. Valve Mounting",
      "refs": [
        {
